title: Sample Book (France), 1850
description: Oversized red cloth bound book with 2,239 French textile samples. Very good condition and quality. Predominantly dark colors and earth tones.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book (France), 1850; paper, printed cotton textile samples; H x W x D: 51.5 × 35 × 8.5 cm (20 1/4 × 13 3/4 × 3 3/8 in.); Gift of Virginia Hamill Johnson; 1973-6-8
